branchCategory.name: CQM
branchCategory.description: <P>The CQM is a compact cylinder integrated with a guide rod and plate. The series is available in 12, 16, 20, 25, 32, 40, 50, 63, 80, and 100mm bore sizes. Non-rotating accuracy is 0.2 or less.  Series CQM allows a workpiece to be mounted directly to the tooling plate.  Auto switches are mountable/removable even when the plate is retracted.</P>
